### 0.6.2
Improve Job handling  by adding ClosureJob to use triggerNow of quartz and offering log file instead of database log
field, toggle it on by setting logFileName property to a filename.
jobLogDir can indicate the directory to save log files, default is './' .

### 0.6.1
Supporting JNDI data source (url must start with java:)
remove #status style as it affects status fields view
Fix passwordComplexity non-default value string to regex issue
Update show.gsp template labels to use message tag

### 0.5.4
Add file ajax upload to dialog forms
Add MSSQLServer support in domain classes and table column
Introducing config grails.plugin.rira.mssqlserver as boolean to enable support of MSSQLServer
Add app.css as application wide css that apply in layout level
Add hideMenu Konfig as default behavior if menu parameter or session item not exist


